‚öôÔ∏è Technical Layer: Is Politeness a Waste of Compute?

On a purely computational level, politeness barely registers. A few extra tokens like ‚Äúplease,‚Äù ‚Äúthank you,‚Äù or ‚Äúhello‚Äù are negligible compared to:

Multimodal tasks (e.g., generating a Ghibli-style image)

